articles.author: Rebecca Rubin
articles.title: Box Office: John Krasinski’s ‘IF’ Debuts at No. 1 With Soft $35 Million - Variety
articles.description: John Krasinski's "IF" fell slightly short of box office expectations but still topped the North American charts.
articles.content:
Not exactly the opening weekend that dreams are made of.
